WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language:  en

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:14.000
... So please, behave yourselves.
You are well educated people. So control you

00:00:14.100 --> 00:00:19.379
emotions
There are basic things

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:28.530
There is history
Which you will learn later

00:00:28.530 --> 00:00:40.000
Above this building was flag of Russia
Above this building was flag of USSR

00:00:40.800 --> 00:00:48.500
Above this building was flag of Ukraine
But this is history

00:00:48.560 --> 00:00:55.560
Today, factually, legally.. any way you like
it

00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:04.190
University has transitioned under command
of Russian Federation.

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:16.190
Comrade students, I never divide the nationalities,
but only by gender.

00:01:17.760 --> 00:01:25.760
Young man, Young woman.
Everything else is a fiction of bad people.

00:01:25.760 --> 00:01:41.899
We are all Slavic
So, let's together, calmly, in this hour,

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:48.820
which will be recorded in the history of Ukraine
and Russia

00:01:49.090 --> 00:01:57.090
and spend it with dignity.
National flag of Ukraine....

00:01:59.280 --> 00:02:20.390
Anthem?...
[Ukrainian Anthem playing]

00:03:21.390 --> 00:03:26.390
[Ukrainian Anthem is cut short]
National Flag of Ukraine - out.

00:03:26.400 --> 00:03:30.360
[Students continue singing the anthem]

00:03:31.360 --> 00:03:35.360
Anthem is already finished! Listen!
Or the bear has stepped on your ears?

00:03:46.180 --> 00:04:09.180
[Chanting: Glory to Ukraine!Glory to Heroes]
The national flag of Russian Federation, Raise!

00:04:09.750 --> 00:06:06.660
[Russian Anthem playing]
[Students leaving the square in defiant move]

00:06:10.660 --> 00:06:14.660
Thank you everybody
And now I see

00:06:15.000 --> 00:06:20.900
Ethical education of people
Throughout the times

00:06:21.000 --> 00:06:27.430
Always, in every countries, when the anthem
is playing

00:06:30.000 --> 00:06:35.139
Everyone behaves.
And actually stand straight [reference to military stand]

00:06:37.009 --> 00:06:39.800
You yourself have seen now

00:06:39.800 --> 00:06:44.710
education of the people.
This saddens me.

00:06:45.710 --> 00:06:51.000
And this is worrying
Thank you to all

